\sum_{k=1}^\infty \frac{(k!)^2}{(2k)!}
(k+1)!=k!(k+1)
(2(k+1))!
2(k+1)=2k+2
k+1
\bigl(2(k+1)\bigr)!=(2k+2)!=(2k+2)(2k+1)(2k)!.
\frac{\bigl((k+1)!\bigr)^2}{(k!)^2}=\left(\frac{(k+1)!}{k!}\right)^2=\left(\frac{k!(k+1)}{k!}\right)^2=(k+1)^2,
\frac{((k+1)!)^2}{(2(k+1))!} \frac{(2k)!}{(k!)^2}=\frac{(k+1)^2}{(2k+1)(2k+2)}\xrightarrow [k\to\infty]{}\frac{1}{4}
